wikipedia_page.main: Richard Liburd (born 26 September 1973) is an English footballer who is a defender who last played for Hucknall Town. He previously played league football with Middlesbrough, Bradford City, Carlisle United, Notts County and Lincoln City.

link_mentions.page: List of Bradford City A.F.C. players

response: Richard Liburd played professionally for Notts County and Bradford City.  Matt Redmile played for Shrewsbury Town.  Miles Addison played for Derby County.
